title: Thank god the Test ended due to bad light: Former Pakistan players slam team’s poor show on final day
text: Thank god the Test ended due to bad light: Former Pakistan players slam team’s poor show on final day Sunday, 18 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) Pakistan fell for 173 leaving England requiring 99 runs for victory on a dramatic day.
